OL,3,CTwo more charged following Old Firm
OL,4,Cdisorder
OL,6,FTwo more people have been charged in
OL,7,Fconnection with disorder at a Scottish
OL,8,FCup tie between Rangers and Celtic
OL,9,Flast month.
OL,11,FSeveral officers and members of the
OL,12,Fpublic were injured after fans invaded
OL,13,Fthe pitch in the immediate aftermath
OL,14,Fof Celtic's penalty shootout victory
OL,15,Fover their Glasgow rivals on March 8.
OL,17,FDozens of travelling Celtic fans
OL,18,Fspilled onto the pitch to celebrate
OL,19,Fand more than 100 Rangers fans charged
OL,20,Fto confront them.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/4
