OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777255442
OL,3,CTwo more charged following Old Firm
OL,4,Cdisorder
OL,6,FPolice and stewards formed a barrier
OL,7,Fto prevent large-scale interaction but
OL,8,Fthere was violence and missiles,
OL,9,Fincluding a lit flare, were thrown.
OL,11,FPolice said a 10-year-old child had
OL,12,Fbeen hit by a coin and one officer was
OL,13,Fhit on the head by a bottle.
OL,15,FFootage also showed a female officer
OL,16,Fbeing kicked to the ground from behind
OL,17,Fby a Rangers fan who was sprinting
OL,18,Ftowards the Broomloan stand, which
OL,19,Fheld 7,500 Celtic supporters.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/4
