OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777255442
OL,3,CTwo more charged following Old Firm
OL,4,Cdisorder
OL,6,FPolice have already made a number of
OL,7,Farrests as part of Operation
OL,8,FMoonglint, which was launched to
OL,9,Finvestigate the disorder and identify
OL,10,Fthose involved.
OL,12,FOn Sunday, police confirmed that two
OL,13,Ffurther men, aged 18 and 19, have been
OL,14,Farrested and charged with various
OL,15,Foffences in relation to the disorder.
OL,17,FThey are due to appear in court in due
OL,18,Fcourse.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/4
