OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1777255442
OL,3,CTwo more charged following Old Firm
OL,4,Cdisorder
OL,6,FDetective Chief Inspector David Lamont
OL,7,Fpreviously said: "Extensive inquiries
OL,8,Fare ongoing to identify and trace
OL,9,Fthose involved in the scenes which
OL,10,Ftook place at the conclusion of the
OL,11,Fmatch on Sunday March 8.
OL,13,F"A team of officers continue to carry
OL,14,Fout inquiries and examine a large
OL,15,Famount of CCTV images and footage to
OL,16,Fidentify and trace those involved,
OL,17,Ffurther arrests will be made."
OL,19,FAnyone with information can call 101
OL,20,For contact Crimestoppers anonymously
OL,21,Fon 0800 555 111.
